{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7764bd0f1a","title":"江青对送审翻译影片的意见","origin":"文化部办公厅提供","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b940cd17b1","index":0,"year":1976,"month":5,"day":23,"articleId":"7764bd0f1a"}],"tags":[{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5cca8cf689","type":"title","text":"江青对送审翻译影片的意见","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7764bd0f1a"},{"id":"1773146787","type":"authors","text":"江青","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7764bd0f1a"},{"id":"d740bd6823","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七六年五月二十三日晚，刘玉廷电话传达江青的以下意见：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7764bd0f1a"},{"id":"3783fbe489","type":"paragraph","text":"凡是过去我审定送去翻译的电影，译好应该先送我，不是送远新同志。今后由远新同志通知你们审定去翻译的片子，翻译后也要送我。因为这也是由我审定的，我只是不审查第一关。因为那个范围太大了，我只看远新同志向我推荐的。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7764bd0f1a"},{"id":"4900f8182c","type":"paragraph","text":"另外，送远新同志看的电影，也电话告诉我一下电影目录。《醒目狗》何时送？《新茶花女》、《痴女幽魂》、《砂丘之女》都送给远新同志。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7764bd0f1a"},{"id":"2594fb347e","type":"paragraph","text":"请抄报春桥同志。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7764bd0f1a"},{"id":"432946a7af","type":"appellation","text":"（文化部办公厅提供）","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7764bd0f1a"}],"page":{"id":"55f216a87e","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7764bd0f1a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}